---
title: Speedy Cajun Beef Rice Bowl with Avocado Salsa and Cheese
description: This Speedy Cajun Beef Rice Bowl can be on your table in less than 25 minutes. Punchy and smoky with a spicy kick, Cajun spice mix contains ingredients such as chilli powder, ground cumin, oregano and thyme.
